<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>International&#174; MaxxForce&#8482; DT, 9 and 10 Engine Service Manual - Fuel and High-pressure Oil Systems
        - Removal - High-pressure Oil Pump and Injection Pressure Regulator (IPR) Valve
    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="remove" graphiccount="2">
        <title>High-pressure Oil Pump and Injection Pressure Regulator (IPR) Valve</title>
        <figure id="f3350007186" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figK11/K11036.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="no"/>
            <caption>IPR Removal / Installation Tool</caption>
        </figure>
        <figure id="f3350007175" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figk11/K11006.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="no"/>
            <caption>High-pressure oil pump</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1 type="arabic">M8 x 100 bolt (2)</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">IPR valve magnetic coil</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">IPR valve</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">M8 x 30 bolt (2)</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
        <specpara>
            <note>
                <para>IPR valve magnetic coil rotates separately from the IPR valve.</para>
            </note>
        </specpara>
        <step1>
            <para id="s0710" count="1">Remove IPR valve as follows:</para>
            <randlist type="bullet">
                <item>
                    <para>If the high-pressure oil pump and air compressor are installed, hold the IPR valve magnetic
                        coil stationary while turning the IPR valve to remove from the high-pressure oil pump.
                    </para>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <para>If the high-pressure oil pump or air compressor are not installed, use the
                        <hotlnk document="eges3351_191.xml" xrefid="t335000703" appearance="hottext">IPR Removal /
                            Installation Tool
                        </hotlnk>
                        <xref refid="t335000703"/>
                        to remove IPR valve from the high-pressure oil pump.
                    </para>
                </item>
            </randlist>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove and discard IPR valve O-rings and back-up rings.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove two M8 x 100 and two M8 x 30 bolts holding the high-pressure oil pump to the front
                cover.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the high-pressure oil pump and discard the high-pressure pump gasket.</para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
